  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1041890/extras/89bade262781dbb18b73765b526bb20e.avif?t=1614001852\" width=616 height=64 /></span><br><br><strong>iMemory </strong> - This is a logical game designed to train the memory and attention of the player.<br><br>You have to memorize in what places the correct cards are located, each subsequent level becomes more difficult than the previous one.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Simple controls<br></li><li> Relaxing soundtrack.<br></li><li> Training your brain and attention.<br></li><li> Gameplay for children and adults.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Credits:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Programming:  PlatSTUDIO && AFBIK Studio<br></li><li> Music and effects: zapsplat</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1041890/extras/89bade262781dbb18b73765b526bb20e.avif?t=1614001852\" width=616 height=64 /></span>",
